  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d89\u0d82\u0da2\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca E \u0dc0\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An E wheeler from Peradeniya engineering students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As a solution to the country's fuel problem and in an environmentally friendly way, a group of students from the Faculty of Engineering of the University of Peradeniya have created an electric tricycle.",
        "This tricycle was displayed for the first time when the University of Peradeniya Research Excellence Exhibition - 2022 started today (23rd) at the Integrated Water Research Centre.",
        "Mr. Lilantha Samaranayake, Professor of the Department of Electrical and Electronics Engineering, Faculty of Engineering, University of Peradeniya, introduced the electric tricycle to the media.",
        "The professor says that the electric tricycle known as E Wheeler can travel a distance of 60 kilometers with a single battery charge. The professor has said that when this three-wheeler is started at the business level, two million three-wheelers in the country can be converted to run on electricity.",
        "The peculiarity of this is that the battery used for that purpose does not need to be charged by the owner of the tricycle and a charged battery can be obtained by giving the used battery to the centers established for that purpose across the country in the same way as an empty gas cylinder is used to get a new gas cylinder. Then the professor said that the owner of the three-wheeler will have to pay a certain amount only for its electricity.",
        "Professor Lilantha Samaranayake also said that a private company has come forward to start this project."
      ],
